Usage: set_input_transition [-help] <transition_time> <port_list> [-fall]
                            [-max] [-min] [-rise]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<transition_time>     # Specifies the transition time (float, required)
<port_list>           # List of ports for which the slew time is specified
                      # (string, required)
-fall                 # Slew time should be applied to the falling edge of the
                      # signal (data or clock) (bool, optional)
-max                  # Slew times are with respect to the late (setup) time
                      # check of the data signal (bool, optional)
-min                  # Slew times are with respect to the early (hold) time
                      # check of the data signal (bool, optional)
-rise                 # Slew time should be applied to the rising edge of the
                      # signal (data or clock) (bool, optional)